lity of developer experience you get with Resend.",companyAvatar:"logo-outerbase.jpg",companyName:"Outerbase",authorAvatar:"brandon-strittmatter.jpg",authorName:"Brandon Strittmatter",authorTitle:"Co-founder of Outerbase"},{content:"Resend is an amazing product. It was so easy to switch over. I feel confident knowing that our important emails are in good hands with Resend. Everyone should be using this.",companyAvatar:"logo-ruby-card.jpg",companyName:"Ruby Card",authorAvatar:"shariar-kabir.jpg",authorName:"Shariar Kabir",authorTitle:"Founder at Ruby Card"},{content:"All of our customers are located in South America, so having a solution that could send emails from the region closest to our users is very important. Resend's multi-region feature is a game-changer for us.",companyAvatar:"logo-voa-hoteis.jpg",companyName:"VOA Hoteis",authorAvatar:"giovanni-keppelen.jpg",authorName:"Giovanni Keppelen",authorTitle:"CTO & Partner at VOA Hoteis"},{content:"The speed and ease of integrating with the product was incredible, but what really stood out was their intricate knowledge of email and relentless support day or night. Oh and we also ended up winning Product of the week.",companyAvatar:"logo-anyone.jpg",companyName:"Anyone",authorAvatar:"sam-ducker.jpg",authorName:"Sam Ducker",authorTitle:"Co-founder of Anyone"},{content:"As a developer I love the approach that the Resend team is taking. Its so refreshing. They are also extremely user-centric and helpful in terms of getting you up and running, sending beautiful emails that deliver.",companyAvatar:"logo-mintlify.jpg",companyName:"Mintlify",authorAvatar:"hahnbee-lee.jpg",authorName:"Hahnbee Lee",authorTitle:"Co-Founder at Mintlify"},{content:"The Resend team have built a great product in a space that hasn't seen 10x innovation for years. Engineering peers are raving about Resend - it's such a smoother dev experience.",companyAvatar:"logo-alliance.jpg",companyName:"Alliance",authorAvatar:"roberto-riccio.jpg",authorName:"Rob